{
  "script_id": "mobius",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.89,
      "size": 46224,
      "text": "拿一条纸带，把一端翻转180度，再和另一端粘起来。你就做出了一个莫比乌斯环。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.81,
      "size": 44928,
      "text": "普通的纸带有正反两面，但莫比乌斯环上的蚂蚁，不用翻越边缘就能走遍\"两面\"。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "今天我们就在三维空间里，亲手旋转这些奇妙的拓扑曲面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "mobius",
      "line_id": "mob-1",
      "filename": "mobius-mob-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/mobius-mob-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.88,
      "size": 46080,
      "text": "这就是莫比乌斯环。注意它的扭转：中线绕一圈，带子本身却翻转了半圈。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "mobius",
      "line_id": "mob-2",
      "filename": "mobius-mob-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/mobius-mob-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "让一只蚂蚁沿中线出发，走完一圈，它会发现自己来到了出发点的\"背面\"。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "mobius",
      "line_id": "mob-4",
      "filename": "mobius-mob-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/mobius-mob-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.81,
      "size": 44928,
      "text": "更妙的是：沿中线把它剪开，它不会一分为二，而是变成一个更长的双扭大环。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "klein",
      "line_id": "klein-2",
      "filename": "klein-klein-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/klein-klein-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.07,
      "size": 49104,
      "text": "它是一个没有边界、也没有内外之分的封闭曲面。倒进去的水，分不清是在瓶内还是瓶外。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "klein",
      "line_id": "klein-3",
      "filename": "klein-klein-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/klein-klein-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.92,
      "size": 46800,
      "text": "我们看到的\"瓶颈穿过瓶身\"只是三维的妥协，真正的克莱因瓶完美地存在于四维空间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-1",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/compare-cmp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.19,
      "size": 51120,
      "text": "作为对比，看看普通的环面。它和莫比乌斯环一样是一个圈，却清清楚楚有内外两面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-2",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/compare-cmp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "环面是可定向曲面，而莫比乌斯环和克莱因瓶是不可定向曲面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "cmp-3",
      "filename": "compare-cmp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/compare-cmp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.6,
      "size": 41616,
      "text": "是否可定向，是拓扑学区分曲面的一个根本特征，它不随拉伸弯曲而改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "现在你可以用鼠标拖动，从任意角度旋转这些曲面，仔细观察它们的扭转结构。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "切换莫比乌斯环、克莱因瓶和环面，对比单侧与双侧的差异。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "mobius",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/mobius/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "数学的想象力可以超越我们生活的维度。继续探索吧！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 37.080000000000005,
